title: The BLACK+DECKER POWERSWIVEL Full Size Upright Vacuum
description: Feel the power of clean!  Introducing the POWERSWIVEL upright from BLACK+DECKER®.  Everything that the AIRSWIVEL offers, now with more power!  Multi-cyclonic performance ideal for both carpets and hardwood floors.  Comes with HEPA filtration, on-board pet hair tool to remove stubborn pet hair.
